creator: johlin
title: TailorKey v4.2h - macOS Bilateral Swedish
notes:
TailorKey Mac version 4.2h, modified with:

- Swedish locale with åäö
- Thumb cluster based on Glorious Engrammer, but:
  - No insert
  - No <>, instead mouse scroll
  - Slash and colon (vim search and cmd) on T6
  - Line home/end (Mac-specific)
- Various sybols on base layer adjusted with some more Swedish-aligned keys and some extra symbol keys for programming (brackets and the like)
- Symbol layer fixed for Swedish locale
- Cursor layer adjusted with:
  - No cut/copy/paste on right half
  - Arrow keys shifted one step to the left and swapped up/down to mirror vim
  - Number layer from Glorious Engrammer but adjusted for Swedish locale
- Various RGB adjustments for preference:
  - Adjusted cursor layer to match new arrow placement and dulled home/end/pgup/pgup just below
  - Highlight numbers in numpad (lower layer)
  - Highlight both home row keys when pressed and removed thumb lights due to different thumb cluster layout
- No caps lock on enter or esc
- Caps word on both HRM shifts

holdTaps.description:
AutoShift Helper - &AS main macro is chained to &AS_HT hold tap and &AS_Shifted macro. For faster typists, it is recommended to decrease the tapping-term-ms value. A suggested value is 135 ms.
More: https://github.com/nickcoutsos/keymap-editor/wiki/Autoshift-using-ZMK-behaviors
